#: templates/volunteer_profile.html:152
msgid "Попълни профила си"
msgstr "Complete your profile"

#: templates/volunteer_profile.html:154
msgid ""
"Това е всичко. Когато има заявка, която пасва - ще я видиш в таблото. "
"Няма автоматични ангажименти."
msgstr ""
"That's all. When a request matches, you'll see it in the dashboard. No "
"automatic engagement."

#: templates/volunteer_profile.html:243
msgid "Какво да очакваш"
msgstr "What to expect"

#: templates/volunteer_profile.html:244
msgid ""
"HelpChain не е “чат за всичко”. Показваме ти заявки, ти решаваш дали да "
"помогнеш."
msgstr ""
"HelpChain is not a \"cat for everything\". We show you requests and you "
"choose to help or not."

#: templates/volunteer_profile.html:248
msgid "Няма автоматични ангажименти."
msgstr "No automatic engagement."

#: templates/volunteer_profile.html:249
msgid "Можеш да откажеш без обяснения."
msgstr "You can refuse without explanation."

#: templates/volunteer_profile.html:250
msgid "Личните данни се показват само при нужда/съгласие."
msgstr "Personal data are only displayed if necessary or consent is required."

#: templates/volunteer_profile.html:254
msgid "Съвет:"
msgstr "Tip:"

#: templates/volunteer_profile.html:255
msgid "Ако добавиш точна локация + 2-3 умения, шансът за match се вдига осезаемо."
msgstr ""
"Adding a precise location and 2-3 skills significantly increases match "
"chances."

#: templates/volunteer_request_details.html:2
#: templates/volunteer_request_details.html:28
msgid "Детайли за заявка"
msgstr "Application details"

#: templates/volunteer_request_details.html:18
msgid "Демо: нищо не се записва."
msgstr "Demo: nothing recorded."

#: templates/volunteer_request_details.html:20
msgid "Следва кратък преглед и потвърждение."
msgstr "A brief review and confirmation follow."

#: templates/volunteer_request_details.html:29
msgid "Назад"
msgstr "Return"

#: templates/volunteer_request_details.html:37
msgid "You marked that you can help."
msgstr "You marked that you can help."

#: templates/volunteer_request_details.html:39
msgid "Go to contact"
msgstr "Contact"

#: templates/volunteer_request_details.html:43
msgid "You marked that you can't help right now."
msgstr "You marked that you can't help right now."

#: templates/volunteer_request_details.html:45
#: templates/volunteer_request_details.html:139
msgid "Last signal"
msgstr "Trusted Badges"

#: templates/volunteer_request_details.html:48
msgid "You haven't sent a signal yet."
msgstr "You haven't feel a signal yet."

#: templates/volunteer_request_details.html:53
msgid "Заявка"
msgstr "Request"

#: templates/volunteer_request_details.html:67
msgid "Няма описание."
msgstr "No description."

#: templates/volunteer_request_details.html:91
msgid "Назначен/а"
msgstr "Designated"

#: templates/volunteer_request_details.html:103
msgid ""
"Имаш зелена светлина за тази заявка. Използвай бутоните долу, за да се "
"свържеш с човека."
msgstr ""
"You have the green light for this request. Use the buttons below to "
"contact the person."

#: templates/volunteer_request_details.html:107
msgid "Заявката е изпратена. Ще получиш известие при решение."
msgstr "The request was sent. You will be notified when a decision is made."

#: templates/volunteer_request_details.html:113
msgid ""
"Щом екипът потвърди, ще получиш известие и ще отключим контакта (ако е "
"нужно)."
msgstr ""
"Once the team is confirmed, you will be notified and we will unblock the "
"contact (if necessary)."

#: templates/volunteer_request_details.html:115
msgid ""
"Ти си потвърден/а за тази заявка. Следвай указанията по-долу и действай "
"спокойно."
msgstr ""
"You are confirmed for this request. Follow the instructions below and act"
" calmly."

#: templates/volunteer_request_details.html:117
msgid "Няма проблем — можеш да помогнеш по друга заявка. Благодарим ти."
msgstr "Don't worry, you can help on another request. Thanks."

#: templates/volunteer_request_details.html:119
msgid ""
"Ако можеш да помогнеш, натисни „Мога да помогна“ — това ни дава сигнал да"
" те свържем."
msgstr "If you can help, click on \"I can help\" : it tells us to connect you."

#: templates/volunteer_request_details.html:133
msgid "Твоят сигнал"
msgstr "Your signal"

#: templates/volunteer_request_details.html:135
msgid ""
"Това е бърз сигнал към екипа. Не е обвързващ — помага ни да реагираме "
"по-точно."
msgstr ""
"It's a quick signal to the team. It is not engaging, it helps us to react"
" more precisely."

#: templates/admin/request_details.html:221 templates/admin/requests.html:305
#: templates/volunteer_request_details.html:142
msgid "Can help"
msgstr "You want to help?"

#: templates/admin/request_details.html:223 templates/admin/requests.html:307
#: templates/volunteer_request_details.html:144
msgid "Can't help"
msgstr "You want to help?"

#: templates/volunteer_request_details.html:159
msgid "Мога да помогна"
msgstr "I can help"

#: templates/volunteer_request_details.html:163
msgid "Не мога да помогна"
msgstr "I can't help"

#: templates/volunteer_request_details.html:169
msgid "Ако не можеш — всичко е ок. По-добре честен сигнал, отколкото тишина."
msgstr "If you can't, it's okay. Better an honest signal than silence."

#: templates/volunteer_request_details.html:174
msgid "Изчакване"
msgstr ""

#: templates/volunteer_request_details.html:176
msgid "Потвърдено"
msgstr "Confirmed"

#: templates/volunteer_request_details.html:213
msgid ""
"Използвай този контакт само за тази заявка. Бъди уважителен/а и "
"конкретен/а — това ускорява помощта."
msgstr ""
"Use this contact only for this request. Be respectful and accurate: it "
"speeds up help."

